*Li* se kaže da je ona lepa žena. (It is said that she is a beautiful woman.)

*Li*čno mislim da je ovo dobra ideja. (Personally, I think this is a good idea.)

*Li*čno ne volim da se mešam u tuđe stvari. (Personally, I don't like to meddle in other people's affairs.)

*Li*čno znam da je ona dobra čovek. (I personally know that she is a good person.)

*Li*čno volim da pomažem drugima. (I personally like to help others.)